msgstr "COLUMNS(A1:C3) retorna 3"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5367
#, no-c-format
msgid "COLUMNS(D2) returns 1"
msgstr "COLUMNS(D2) retorna 1"

#. Tag: member
